            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Since this issue also happens in Vim, the problem probably comes from the syntax file rather than from Neovim. You should contact the [syntax files' authors](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/4ae31c46f75aef7d7a80dd2a8d269c168806a1bd/runtime/syntax/yaml.vim#L3-L4) and ask them to fix this issue and send the result to Vim's maintainers as Neovim doesn't maintain its own runtime files - most of them are directly copied from Vim.",
